Summary: This section lists default key mappings for actions in the 2D / CanvasItem editor across different operating systems and their corresponding editor settings.

2D / CanvasItem editor
- Action name: Zoom In. Windows, Linux: Ctrl + =. macOS: Cmd + =. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/zoom_plus.
- Action name: Zoom Out. Windows, Linux: Ctrl + -. macOS: Cmd + -. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/zoom_minus.
- Action name: Zoom Reset. Windows, Linux: Ctrl + 0. macOS: Cmd + 0. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/zoom_reset.
- Action name: Pan View. Windows, Linux: Space. macOS: Space. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/pan_view.
- Action name: Select Mode. Windows, Linux: Q. macOS: Q. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/select_mode.
- Action name: Move Mode. Windows, Linux: W. macOS: W. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/move_mode.
- Action name: Rotate Mode. Windows, Linux: E. macOS: E. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/rotate_mode.
- Action name: Scale Mode. Windows, Linux: S. macOS: S. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/scale_mode.
- Action name: Ruler Mode. Windows, Linux: R. macOS: R. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/ruler_mode.
- Action name: Use Smart Snap. Windows, Linux: Shift + S. macOS: Shift + S. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/use_smart_snap.
- Action name: Use Grid Snap. Windows, Linux: Shift + G. macOS: Shift + G. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/use_grid_snap.
- Action name: Multiply grid step by 2. Windows, Linux: Num *. macOS: Num *. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/multiply_grid_step.
- Action name: Divide grid step by 2. Windows, Linux: Num /. macOS: Num /. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/divide_grid_step.
- Action name: Always Show Grid. Windows, Linux: G. macOS: G. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/show_grid.
- Action name: Show Helpers. Windows, Linux: H. macOS: H. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/show_helpers.
- Action name: Show Guides. Windows, Linux: Y. macOS: Y. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/show_guides.
- Action name: Center Selection. Windows, Linux: F. macOS: F. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/center_selection.
- Action name: Frame Selection. Windows, Linux: Shift + F. macOS: Shift + F. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/frame_selection.
- Action name: Preview Canvas Scale. Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + P. macOS: Cmd + Shift + P. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/preview_canvas_scale.
- Action name: Insert Key. Windows, Linux: Ins. macOS: Ins. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/anim_insert_key.
- Action name: Insert Key (Existing Tracks). Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Ins. macOS: Cmd + Ins. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/anim_insert_key_existing_tracks.
- Action name: Make Custom Bones from Nodes. Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + B. macOS: Cmd + Shift + B. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/skeleton_make_bones.
- Action name: Clear Pose. Windows, Linux: Shift + K. macOS: Shift + K. Editor setting: canvas_item_editor/anim_clear_pose.
