* Freelook Left: A / A. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_left`
* Freelook Right: D / D. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_right`
* Freelook Forward: W / W. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_forward`
* Freelook Backwards: S / S. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_backwards`
* Freelook Up: E / E. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_up`
* Freelook Down: Q / Q. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_down`
* Freelook Speed Modifier: Shift / Shift. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_speed_modifier`
* Freelook Slow Modifier: Alt / Opt. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/freelook_slow_modifier`
* Select Mode: Q / Q. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/tool_select`
* Move Mode: W / W. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/tool_move`
* Rotate Mode: E / E. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/tool_rotate`
* Scale Mode: R / R. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/tool_scale`
* Use Local Space: T / T. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/local_coords`
* Use Snap: Y / Y. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/snap`
* Snap Object to Floor: PgDown / PgDown. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/snap_to_floor`
* Top View: Num 7 / Num 7. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/top_view`
* Bottom View: Alt + Num 7 / Opt + Num 7. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/bottom_view`
* Front View: Num 1 / Num 1. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/front_view`
* Rear View: Alt + Num 1 / Opt + Num 1. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/rear_view`
* Right View: Num 3 / Num 3. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/right_view`
* Left View: Alt + Num 3 / Opt + Num 3. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/left_view`
* Switch Perspective/Orthogonal View: Num 5 / Num 5. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/switch_perspective_orthogonal`
* Insert Animation Key: K / K. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/insert_anim_key`
* Focus Origin: O / O. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/focus_origin`
* Focus Selection: F / F. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/focus_selection`
* Align Transform with View: Ctrl + Alt + M / Opt + Cmd + M. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/align_transform_with_view`
* Align Rotation with View: Ctrl + Alt + F / Opt + Cmd + F. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/align_rotation_with_view`
* 1 Viewport: Ctrl + 1 / Cmd + 1. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/1_viewport`
* 2 Viewports: Ctrl + 2 / Cmd + 2. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/2_viewports`
* 2 Viewports (Alt): Ctrl + Alt + 2 / Opt + Cmd + 2. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/2_viewports_alt`
* 3 Viewports: Ctrl + 3 / Cmd + 3. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/3_viewports`
* 3 Viewports (Alt): Ctrl + Alt + 3 / Opt + Cmd + 3. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/3_viewports_alt`
* 4 Viewports: Ctrl + 4 / Cmd + 4. Editor setting: `spatial_editor/4_viewports`
