*   Find Previous: Windows, Linux: Shift + F3; macOS: Cmd + Shift + G. Editor setting: script_text_editor/find_previous
*   Find in Files: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + F; macOS: Cmd + Shift + F. Editor setting: script_text_editor/find_in_files
*   Replace: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + R; macOS: Opt + Cmd + F. Editor setting: script_text_editor/replace
*   Replace in Files: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + R; macOS: Cmd + Shift + R. Editor setting: script_text_editor/replace_in_files
*   Undo: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Z; macOS: Cmd + Z. Editor setting: script_text_editor/undo
*   Redo: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Y; macOS: Cmd + Y. Editor setting: script_text_editor/redo
*   Move Up: Windows, Linux: Alt + Up Arrow; macOS: Opt + Up Arrow. Editor setting: script_text_editor/move_up
*   Move Down: Windows, Linux: Alt + Down Arrow; macOS: Opt + Down Arrow. Editor setting: script_text_editor/move_down
*   Delete Line: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + K; macOS: Cmd + Shift + K. Editor setting: script_text_editor/delete_line
*   Toggle Comment: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + K; macOS: Cmd + K. Editor setting: script_text_editor/toggle_comment
*   Fold/Unfold Line: Windows, Linux: Alt + F; macOS: Ctrl + Cmd + F. Editor setting: script_text_editor/toggle_fold_line
*   Duplicate Lines: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Alt + Down Arrow; macOS: Cmd + Shift + Down Arrow. Editor setting: script_text_editor/duplicate_lines
*   Duplicate Selection: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + D; macOS: Cmd + Shift + C. Editor setting: script_text_editor/duplicate_selection
