*   Select Up: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + Up Arrow; macOS: Shift + Opt + Up Arrow. Editor setting: common/ui_text_caret_add_above
*   Select Next Occurrence: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + D; macOS: Cmd + D. Editor setting: common/ui_text_add_selection_for_next_occurrence
*   Complete Symbol: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Space; macOS: Ctrl + Space. Editor setting: script_text_editor/complete_symbol
*   Evaluate Selection: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + E; macOS: Cmd + Shift + E. Editor setting: script_text_editor/evaluate_selection
*   Trim Trailing Whitespace: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Alt + T; macOS: Opt + Cmd + T. Editor setting: script_text_editor/trim_trailing_whitespace
*   Uppercase: Windows, Linux: Shift + F4; macOS: Shift + F4. Editor setting: script_text_editor/convert_to_uppercase
*   Lowercase: Windows, Linux: Shift + F5; macOS: Shift + F5. Editor setting: script_text_editor/convert_to_lowercase
*   Capitalize: Windows, Linux: Shift + F6; macOS: Shift + F6. Editor setting: script_text_editor/capitalize
*   Convert Indent to Spaces: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + Y; macOS: Cmd + Shift + Y. Editor setting: script_text_editor/convert_indent_to_spaces
*   Convert Indent to Tabs: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + I; macOS: Cmd + Shift + I. Editor setting: script_text_editor/convert_indent_to_tabs
*   Auto Indent: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + I; macOS: Cmd + I. Editor setting: script_text_editor/auto_indent
*   Toggle Bookmark: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Alt + B; macOS: Opt + Cmd + B. Editor setting: script_text_editor/toggle_bookmark
*   Go to Next Bookmark: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + B; macOS: Cmd + B. Editor setting: script_text_editor/goto_next_bookmark
*   Go to Previous Bookmark: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + B; macOS: Cmd + Shift + B. Editor setting: script_text_editor/goto_previous_bookmark
*   Go to Function: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Alt + F; macOS: Ctrl + Cmd + J. Editor setting: script_text_editor/goto_function
*   Go to Line: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + G; macOS: Cmd + L. Editor setting: script_text_editor/goto_line
*   Toggle Breakpoint: Windows, Linux: F9; macOS: Cmd + Shift + B. Editor setting: script_text_editor/toggle_breakpoint
*   Remove All Breakpoints: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + Shift + F9; macOS: Cmd + Shift + F9. Editor setting: script_text_editor/remove_all_breakpoints
*   Go to Next Breakpoint: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + .; macOS: Cmd + .. Editor setting: script_text_editor/goto_next_breakpoint
*   Go to Previous Breakpoint: Windows, Linux: Ctrl + ,; macOS: Cmd + ,. Editor setting: script_text_editor/goto_previous_breakpoint
*   Contextual Help: Windows, Linux: Alt + F1; macOS: Opt + Shift + Space. Editor setting: script_text_editor/contextual_help
