Document: Script editor
Path: godot/tutorials/editor/default_key_mapping.rst
Summary: This section lists default key mappings for actions within the Godot script editor.

*   Find: Ctrl + F (Windows, Linux), Cmd + F (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/find`.
*   Find Next: F3 (Windows, Linux), F3 (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/find_next`.
*   Find Previous: Shift + F3 (Windows, Linux), Shift + F3 (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/find_previous`.
*   Find in Files: Ctrl + Shift + F (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + F (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/find_in_files`.
*   Move Up: Shift + Alt + Up Arrow (Windows, Linux), Shift + Opt + Up Arrow (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/window_move_up`.
*   Move Down: Shift + Alt + Down Arrow (Windows, Linux), Shift + Opt + Down Arrow (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/window_move_down`.
*   Next Script: Ctrl + Shift + . (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + . (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/next_script`.
*   Previous Script: Ctrl + Shift + , (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + , (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/prev_script`.
*   Reopen Closed Script: Ctrl + Shift + T (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + T (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/reopen_closed_script`.
*   Save: Ctrl + Alt + S (Windows, Linux), Opt + Cmd + S (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/save`.
*   Save All: Ctrl + Shift + Alt + S (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + Opt + S (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/save_all`.
*   Soft Reload Script: Ctrl + Shift + R (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + R (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/reload_script_soft`.
*   History Previous: Alt + Left Arrow (Windows, Linux), Opt + Left Arrow (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/history_previous`.
*   History Next: Alt + Right Arrow (Windows, Linux), Opt + Right Arrow (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/history_next`.
*   Close: Ctrl + W (Windows, Linux), Cmd + W (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/close_file`.
*   Run: Ctrl + Shift + X (Windows, Linux), Cmd + Shift + X (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/run_file`.
*   Toggle Scripts Panel: Ctrl + \ (Windows, Linux), Cmd + \ (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/toggle_scripts_panel`.
*   Zoom In: Ctrl + = (Windows, Linux), Cmd + = (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/zoom_in`.
*   Zoom Out: Ctrl + - (Windows, Linux), Cmd + - (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/zoom_out`.
*   Reset Zoom: Ctrl + 0 (Windows, Linux), Cmd + 0 (macOS). Editor setting: `script_editor/reset_zoom`.
