Document: Default Key Mapping
Path: godot/tutorials/editor/default_key_mapping.rst
Summary: This section lists default key mappings for actions within the Godot Project Manager.

Project manager actions and their default key mappings:
*   New Project (Ctrl + N / Cmd + N): Editor setting project_manager/new_project
*   Import Project (Ctrl + I / Cmd + I): Editor setting project_manager/import_project
*   Scan for Projects (Ctrl + S / Cmd + S): Editor setting project_manager/scan_projects
*   Edit Project (Ctrl + E / Cmd + E): Editor setting project_manager/edit_project
*   Run Project (Ctrl + R / Cmd + R): Editor setting project_manager/run_project
*   Rename Project (F2 / Enter): Editor setting project_manager/rename_project
*   Remove Project (Delete / Cmd + BkSp): Editor setting project_manager/remove_project